Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda - add power states information in proc
Git-commit: ce63f3ba256a48023b425a4a6792f8da03d00948
Patch-mainline: 3.6-rc1
References: bnc#801713

add more power states information:
- reset status
- clock stop ok
- power states error

Output like:
Power: setting=D0, actual=D0, Error, Clock-stop-OK, Setting-reset

Signed-off-by: Wang Xingchao <xingchao.wang@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

